==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Benedicite
<hw>Ben`e*dic"i*te</hw>, <pos>interj.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Benedicite</er>, <pos>n.</pos>]</ety> <def>An exclamation
corresponding to <xex>Bless you</xex> !.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

